al audit right\n  - Termination & renewal: 12-month term, auto-renew unless 60-day notice\n- Decisions made / outcome:\n  - Agreed price: $X/month (approved)\n  - SLA: 99.9% uptime with defined credits\n  - Vendor will provide SOC 2 report and accept audit right limited to production environment\n- Action items:\n  - Ben to draft contract with agreed terms by 3/2 (owner: Ben)\n  - Terry to provide SOC 2 report and technical annex by 3/1 (owner: Terry)\n  - Li to prepare technical checklist for onboarding by 3/5 (owner: Li)\n- Open issues & risks:\n  - Need to confirm disaster recovery RTO/RPO specifics\n  - Risk: onboarding resources may be constrained in April\n- Next steps / follow-up:\n  - Legal sends draft; schedule signature call week of 3/8\n\nTell me which level of detail you want and either paste the call notes or answer a few quick questions (participants, date/time, main outcomes, next steps) and I’ll produce a final one-page summary.",
